snippet.title: Mario a plumber in time - F3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome both loyal viewers and those comming from F3!
If you're reading this right now then you're most likely interested in trying out the new demo for Mario a plumber in time!

Well, I won't keep you waiting, here are the download links! One for google drive...
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hWhVbWwSFHL_OknJGTTkw_8VDSKyLT6M/view?usp=sharing

And another for Drop Box.
https://www.dropbox.com/s/9dv3rjf0ikx2xze/Plumber%20in%20time%20F3%20Demo%20things.zip?dl=0

Like I said last time, please report any bugs or gameplay issues in the comments of this video, It helps me improve the hacks quality tenfold.
And of course, you may be credited if you wish too, just let me know in your comment.

One last thing, as this is a demo, the last level is 6-4, everything beyond that is either form the older version or just broken, so I highly advise against using any Game Genie codes to try and reach the next levels.

I'm not sure if there's much else I need to say, so I'll end it here.
Thank you very much for watching, please do subscribe if this caught your interest and share with others! it'll help me out a lot!

Until then, see you next time!
